# Task and TaskGroup Catalog

## Task Groups

Task Groups organize related tasks into logical units with coordinated execution:

### Deployment and Installation
- **DeploymentTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/deployment_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/deployment_group.rs) - Manages cluster deployment operations
- **InstallDBTaskGroup**: Group for database installation tasks
- **InstallDepPkgTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/install_dep_pkg.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/install_dep_pkg.rs) - Installs required dependency packages
- **BootstrapTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/bootstrap_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/bootstrap_group.rs) - Bootstraps initial cluster setup

### Control Operations
- **ProxyTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/proxy_ctl_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/proxy_ctl_group.rs) - Manages proxy service operations
- **CtrlDBTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/db_cluster_ctrl_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/db_cluster_ctrl_group.rs) - Controls database cluster operations (start/stop/status)
- **MonitorCtlTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/monitor_ctl_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/monitor_ctl_group.rs) - Controls monitoring components
- **LogServiceCtlTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/log_srv_ctl_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/log_srv_ctl_group.rs) - Manages log service components

### Cluster Management
- **ScaleTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/scale_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/scale_group.rs) - Handles cluster scaling operations (add/remove nodes)
- **ScaleLogTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/scale_log_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/scale_log_group.rs) - Manages log scale operations
- **FailoverTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/failover_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/failover_group.rs) - Coordinates failover processes
- **LaunchTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/launch_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/launch_group.rs) - Launches cluster services
- **RemoveTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/remove_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/remove_group.rs) - Removes cluster components

### Maintenance
- **UpdateClusterTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/update_cluster_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/update_cluster_group.rs) - Updates cluster software
- **UpdateConfigTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/update_config_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/update_config_group.rs) - Updates configuration
- **BackupTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/backup_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/backup_group.rs) - Manages backup operations
- **CheckTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/check_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/check_group.rs) - Performs system checks
- **CustomCmdTaskGroup**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/custom_cmd_group.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/group/custom_cmd_group.rs) - Executes custom commands

## Tasks

Individual task implementations that perform specific operations(reuse these tasks as much as possible), one xxx_task.rs file should only implement one type of task, do not try to create or insert multiple tasks inside one xxx_task.rs file, always insert multiple tasks to xxx_group.rs file:

### Database Operations
- **MonographTxCtlTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/monograph_tx_ctl_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/monograph_tx_ctl_task.rs) - Controls MonographDB transaction nodes
- **MonographBootstrapTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/monograph_bootstrap_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/monograph_bootstrap_task.rs) - Bootstraps MonographDB instances
- **TxConfUpdateTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/tx_conf_update_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/tx_conf_update_task.rs) - Updates transaction configuration
- **CassandraCtlTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/cassandra_ctl_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/cassandra_ctl_task.rs) - Controls Cassandra instances
- **CassandraOpTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/cassandra_op_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/cassandra_op_task.rs) - Performs Cassandra operations
- **DbUpdateTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/db_update_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/db_update_task.rs) - Updates database configurations
- **RedisOpTask**: [src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/redis_op_task.rs](mdc:src/cluster_mgr/src/cli/task/redis_op_task.rs) - Manages Redis operations

### Scaling and Topology
